  "description": "<p>市场研究与分析公司IDC表示，智能设备出货量将在2014年到达17亿台。<strong>在这其中，约有10亿会由包括中国、印度、巴西和俄罗斯在内的新兴市场买单。 在这4个国家的联合出货量会超过6.63亿台，市场价值达到2060亿美元，超过美国、英国和日本的4亿出货量与2040亿总价值。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2effec80/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245582.htm&amp;t=IDC%EF%BC%9A2014%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE17%E4%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245582.htm&amp;t=IDC%EF%BC%9A2014%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE17%E4%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245582.htm&amp;t=IDC%EF%BC%9A2014%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE17%E4%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245582.htm&amp;t=IDC%EF%BC%9A2014%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE17%E4%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245582.htm&amp;t=IDC%EF%BC%9A2014%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE17%E4%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://r